{"tid":2029064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人想反中，一定會跟隨美國步伐","createTime":"2020-05-22T05:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T18:26:43.000Z","uid":267881,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"577364c30f74ddac909d1b1f98948c990315978a","tid":2029064,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"上年佢哋仲心存繞倖可以同中共達成協議<br />\n<br />\n但必須承認呢個諗法係太天真，自欺欺人<br />\n<br />\n攬炒已經係最低消費，浴火重生係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅情況下<br />\n<br />\n反中派會加入以美國為首嘅反共陣型<br />\n<br />\n聯合全球反共勢力協調部署：<br />\n-在海外成立臨時政府<br />\n-充工海外資產、取消居留權<br />\n-國際黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n真係擔心祖國會頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申，祝共產黨一統天下，千秋萬世</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c4de137abdc94ff67c74243e1ed415fbd9b47dd","tid":2029064,"uid":6980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"只要侵侵連任到<br />\n一定會用更強硬手段對支共<br />\ngod bless trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca63f6f662388bcb2cf4f6fb6f8417c2eec74bf","tid":2029064,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}